No Fixed Address is the eighth studio album from Canadian rock band Nickelback. It was released on November 14, 2014 in Australia via Republic Records. The album release coincides with the 6 year anniversary of their sixth studio album, Dark Horse. The album is preceded by the lead single "Edge of a Revolution", which was released on August 18, 2014. This is the band's first release on Republic Records, after leaving long-time record label Roadrunner Records in 2013.
